Class MsgAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.xuset.objectIO.markupMsg.MsgAttribute

  • public class MsgAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used by MarkupMsg for attributes. A MsgAttribute has a name, and value field.
